                            <div class="formula-box">
                                <div class="formula-title">Variance for g Generations Apart</div>
                                <div class="formula-main">Var(kÃÇ‚ÇÅ, l) = w<sub>g-1</sub>(l)</div>
                                <div class="formula-note">where w<sub>n</sub>(l) is the integration function over chromosome length l</div>
