                            <strong>Examples:</strong>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Parent-offspring: Var = 0 (no variation)</li>
                                <li>Grandparent-grandchild: Var = w‚ÇÅ(l)</li>
                                <li>Great-grandparent: Var = w‚ÇÇ(l)</li>
                            </ul>
